| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6594 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 29c599d4-f77b-549d-9057-af68889a66cd"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
